            <h2>DNS手動修改</h2>
            <p>請試試下方的步驟，為您排解問題</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ben_menu">
            <a href="ClearDNS_File_zb.html">windows XP</a>
            <a href="ClearDNS_File_za.html">windows 7</a>
            <a href="ClearDNS_File_zc.html" style="background-color:#0E0E0E; color:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #FFF;">windows 8.1</a>
            <a href="ClearDNS_File_zd.html">windows 10</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="CearCachel">
        <div class="Text_A1" style="top: 175px;">開啟 "<strong>設定</strong>"</div>
        <div class="Text_A2" style="top: 625px;">選擇 "<strong>控制面板</strong>"</div>
        <div class="Text_A3" style="top: 1065px;">選擇 "<strong>網路和共享中心</strong>"</div>
        <div class="Text_A4" style="top: 1410px;">點選 "<strong>本地連線</strong>"</div>
        <div class="Text_A5" style="top: 1755px;">開啟本地連線的介面後
            <br />點選 "<strong>屬性(P)</strong>"</div>
        <div class="Text_A6" style="top: 2100px;">開啟屬性(P)的介面後
            <br />勾選 "<strong>Internet 協議版本 4 (TCP/IPv4)</strong>"
            <br />點選 "<strong>屬性(R)</strong>"</div>
        <div class="Text_A7" style="top: 2815px;">開啟屬性(R)的介面後
            <br />選擇 "<strong>使用下面的 DNS 伺服器地址(E)</strong>"，
            <br />並修改:
            <br/>首選DNS伺服器(P): <strong>8 . 8 . 8 . 8</strong>
            <br /> 備用DNS伺服器(A): <strong>8 . 8 . 4 . 4</strong>
            <br />點選 "<strong>確定</strong>"即完成DNS設定。</div>
